---
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<Layout title="About - Dilli Bhaskar">
  <section class="relative z-20 max-w-4xl mx-auto my-12 px-7 lg:px-0">

    <h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">About Me</h1>

    <p class="mb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      My research lies at the intersection of robotics, reinforcement learning, and control theory. 
      I am interested in developing learning algorithms that enable robots to understand and interact 
      with the physical world in a reliable and data-efficient manner. In particular, I study how 
      modern machine learning approaches such as reinforcement learning and world models can be 
      combined with structure from classical physics and control to build autonomous systems that 
      are both physically grounded and robust in real-world environments.
    </p>

    <!-- Education -->
    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4 text-xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-100" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Education</h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0"><img src="/assets/images/experiences/ubc_logo.png" alt="UBC" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-white" /></div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold dark:text-neutral-100">M.A.Sc in Electrical and Computer Engineering</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">University of British Columbia (UBC), Vancouver, CA</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">Sep. 2025 – Aug. 2027 · Advisor: <a href="https://ece.ubc.ca/cyrus-neary/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Prof. Cyrus Neary</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0"><img src="/assets/images/experiences/TCE-Madurai-Logo.png" alt="TCE" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-white" /></div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold dark:text-neutral-100">B.E. in Mechanical Engineering</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Thiagarajar College of Engineering (TCE), Madurai, IN</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">Aug. 2020 – April 2024 · CGPA: 9.02/10.00 (First Class with Distinction)</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">Department Best Outgoing Student · Advisor: <a href="https://scholar.google.co.in/citations?user=_cpaQAgAAAAJ&hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Prof. S. Saravana Perumal</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Research Experience -->
    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4 text-xl font-bold dark:text-neutral-100" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Research Experience</h2>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <img src="/assets/images/experiences/IIT-Madras-Logo.png" alt="IIT Madras" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-white" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold dark:text-neutral-100">Project Associate</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Indian Institute of Technology Madras, Chennai</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-500">July 2024 – Present · Advisor: <a href="https://ed.iitm.ac.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Prof. Chandrashekar Lakshminarayanan</a></p>
          <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 list-disc list-inside">
            <li>Development of Deep RL based pursuit evasion solver with fixed wing UAV agents.</li>
            <li>Fighter pilot behavior cloning for Deep RL based aerobatic maneuvers.</li>
            <li>Rendering the simulations in Unreal Engine.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
          <img src="/assets/images/experiences/iitpkd.jpeg" alt="IIT Palakkad" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 bg-white" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold dark:text-neutral-100">Research Intern</h3>
